Copy the default Dark theme, give it a name and make these following changes in Text Editor's "Font & Colors" section:

primitive type  : #efe97d
keyword         : #e08c47
type/enumeration: #83bdcf
function        : #f6f080   BOLD
virtual function: #f6f080   BOLD Italic
local/field     : #dedede
string          : #899096
preprocessor    : #96f5cb
comment         : #575d61
occurances      : #999999
current line num: #ffffff
